      "created_at": "2025-02-17T20:32:11.719Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi!</p>\n<p>Found an easily reproducible issue (Galaxy S22+) with my Direto X and resistance mode : if I change from erg to resistance mode (i.e slope mode disabled in settings) during a workout, I can never get back to erg mode. The trainer is stuck in resistance mode until I restart the app. Nothing else helps in getting the erg working again.</p>\n<p>If I have the slope sim mode enabled, that works however as expected and I can get back to erg mode. I.e this problem seems to only affect resistance mode (I like to use resistance mode in some longer MMP tests because it offers more fine-grained resistance control than slope mode).</p>\n<p>Being a dev with some knowledge about Android development, I did some debugging with Logcat and the app seems to go into some infinite command queue loop like this when I click the resistance mode button:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/68b3e7542ee1ef2c9b68dfda13ee23b757a2b799.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/68b3e7542ee1ef2c9b68dfda13ee23b757a2b799\" title=\"kuva\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/68b3e7542ee1ef2c9b68dfda13ee23b757a2b799_2_690x234.jpeg\" alt=\"kuva\" data-base62-sha1=\"eWf67ismsFRghlGcaeuKYg6VxXP\" width=\"690\" height=\"234\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/68b3e7542ee1ef2c9b68dfda13ee23b757a2b799_2_690x234.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/68b3e7542ee1ef2c9b68dfda13ee23b757a2b799_2_1035x351.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/68b3e7542ee1ef2c9b68dfda13ee23b757a2b799_2_1380x468.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"2B2C2F\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">kuva</span><span class=\"informations\">1500\u00d7509 94.6 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>This erg \u2192 resistance \u2192 erg works just fine with TR app.</p>",
